section#services.fullheight.parallax
  .container
    h1.contrast Timber Framing Services
    .row
      .twelve.columns.services.offset-by-two
        p For me, timber framing is a fascinating blend of right and left brain, of structure and form.  Whether I'm sharing information in a class, designing a frame &amp; producing shop drawings for an owner-builder, or cutting joinery myself, I'm always focused on creating a structure of lasting beauty.
    .row
      .five.columns.service
        h2 EDUCATION
        javascript:
          window.ecount = 0;
        .circled.sm
          img src='/assets/img/education0.jpg' onclick="window.ecount++; if(window.ecount > 3) {window.ecount=0} this.src='/assets/img/education'+window.ecount+'.jpg';"
        p Teaching classes in basic and Norwegian style Grindbygg framing at <a href='http://northhouse.org/'>North House Folk School</a> and elsewhere.
      .six.columns.service
        h2 DESIGN
        javascript:
          window.dcount = 0;
        .circled.sm
          img src='/assets/img/design0.jpg' onclick="window.dcount++; if(window.dcount > 3) {window.dcount=0} this.src='/assets/img/design'+window.dcount+'.jpg';"
